The model allows identification of reactions which indirectly use oxygen, thereby resulting in limited survival under micro-oxic conditions. To identify additional limitations, we performed two independent in silico analyses: GSM simulations and domainome, comparative genomic analysis. The GSM simulation approach focused on identifying essential \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
