				\begin{document}$$\text {O}_2$$\end{document}O2-dependent metabolic reactions in iJP962, whereas the comparative genomics approach focused on pinpointing the genetic differences between obligate aerobic P. putida strains and other facultative anaerobic Pseudomonas species (Fig. 1). To identify reactions in the GSM that involve \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
